---
// Assumes shared/tokens/tokens.css is already loaded by the page/layout.
// The ASCII words are decorative (aria-hidden); the name is exposed to
// assistive tech via the visually-hidden label. The default slot renders
// alongside the "Schenzle" word (above it on tablet+), letting the layout
// tuck intro copy into the whitespace beside the smaller word.
---

<div class="name-banner">
	<span class="name-banner__sr">Mark Schenzle</span>
	<pre class="name-banner__line name-banner__first" aria-hidden="true">███╗   ███╗ █████╗ ██████╗ ██╗  ██╗
████╗ ████║██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██║ ██╔╝
██╔████╔██║███████║██████╔╝█████╔╝
██║╚██╔╝██║██╔══██║██╔══██╗██╔═██╗
██║ ╚═╝ ██║██║  ██║██║  ██║██║  ██╗
╚═╝     ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝</pre>
	<div class="name-banner__side">
		<div class="name-banner__aside"><slot /></div>
		<pre class="name-banner__line name-banner__last" aria-hidden="true">███████╗ ██████╗██╗  ██╗███████╗███╗   ██╗███████╗██╗     ███████╗
██╔════╝██╔════╝██║  ██║██╔════╝████╗  ██║╚══███╔╝██║     ██╔════╝
███████╗██║     ███████║█████╗  ██╔██╗ ██║  ███╔╝ ██║     █████╗
╚════██║██║     ██╔══██║██╔══╝  ██║╚██╗██║ ███╔╝  ██║     ██╔══╝
███████║╚██████╗██║  ██║███████╗██║ ╚████║███████╗███████╗███████╗
╚══════╝ ╚═════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚══════╝</pre>
	</div>
</div>

<style>
	.name-banner {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-2);
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
		line-height: var(--line-height-tight);
	}

	/* Visually-hidden accessible name for the decorative ASCII art. */
	.name-banner__sr {
		position: absolute;
		width: 1px;
		height: 1px;
		padding: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
		white-space: nowrap;
		border: 0;
		clip-path: inset(50%);
	}

	.name-banner__side {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-2);
		min-width: 0;
	}

	/* Small screens: the intro copy sits below the stacked name. */
	.name-banner__aside {
		order: 1;
	}

	.name-banner__line {
		min-width: 0;
		margin: 0;
		overflow-x: auto;
		white-space: pre;
	}

	.name-banner__first {
		font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.name-banner__last {
		font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	/* From tablet up, "Mark" sits to the left of the "Schenzle" column, and
	   the intro copy tucks into the whitespace directly above that smaller
	   word. Bottom-align so the two words share a common baseline. */
	@media (--bp-md) {
		.name-banner {
			flex-direction: row;
			align-items: flex-end;
			gap: var(--space-4);
		}

		.name-banner__aside {
			order: -1;
		}

		.name-banner__first {
			font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
		}

		.name-banner__last {
			font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
		}
	}

	@media (--bp-lg) {
		.name-banner__first {
			font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
		}

		.name-banner__last {
			font-size: var(--font-size-md);
		}
	}
</style>
